entries.s_10: I am sure lucky that you are a professional, or I wouldn't be here to tell you about it. I'll go see if Han is still busy... hmmm? Oh, you are to be going to Han now.
entries.s_15: Assistance has been offered, but a denial will ensue with gracious attachment. A thought comes to my mind that entails the visitation of Corellia.
entries.s_20: When I was landing the Falcon in a safer, more secret hiding place, I noticed a small craft landing nearby our location. Well, I fear to say, but I have someone after me, and you might want to take care of it before they find us.
entries.s_32: Problems are had by myself concerning a parts of a to be shifted linguistic decoder that was taken by a regional pirate band. Appreciation will be granted upon the finality of your agenda. Hastened movement will increase the feelings of gratitude.
entries.s_34: Hello to your person. The Regal One has messaged your expectation of arrival. Problems are had by myself concerning a parts of a to be shifted linguistic decoder that was taken by a regional pirate band. A request is made for your help. Are you understanding?
entries.s_38: Relief is greatly filling me. Appreciation will be granted upon the finality of your agenda. Hastened movement will increase the feelings of gratitude.
entries.s_43: Assistance has been offered, but a denial will ensue with gracious attachment unless you are of active duty.
